## Monetag configuration (recommended)
# These should be set in Vercel: Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# Example placeholders (do NOT commit real keys here):
# VITE_AD_PROVIDER=monetag
# VITE_MONETAG_ENABLED=true
# VITE_MONETAG_DOMAIN=5gvci.com
# VITE_MONETAG_ZONE_ID=11076770
# VITE_MONETAG_ZONE_1=11076796
# VITE_MONETAG_ZONE_2=244413

# If you previously used Adsterra, the Adsterra variables were removed to
# avoid injecting raw third-party scripts from environment variables at
# build time. Add Monetag keys above in Vercel instead.
